vided in this specification\"> version ?2.23.1</span><table class=\"none\"><tr><td style=\"white-space:nowrap\"><b>Code</b></td><td><b>Display</b></td><td><b>Definition</b></td></tr><tr><td><a href=\"CodeSystem-TreatmentUnspecified.html#TreatmentUnspecified-g_csf\">g_csf</a></td><td>G-CSF</td><td>G-CSF</td></tr><tr><td><a href=\"CodeSystem-TreatmentUnspecified.html#TreatmentUnspecified-iron_chelated\">iron_chelated</a></td><td>Jernkelerende behandling</td><td>Iron chelated / Jernkelerende behandling</td></tr><tr><td><a href=\"CodeSystem-TreatmentUnspecified.html#TreatmentUnspecified-demethylating\">demethylating</a></td><td>Demethylerende behandling</td><td>Demethylating treatment / Demethylerende behandling</td></tr><tr><td><a href=\"CodeSystem-TreatmentUnspecified.html#TreatmentUnspecified-chemotherapi_aml\">chemotherapi_aml</a></td><td>AML lignende kemoterapi</td><td>AML-like chemotherapy / AML lignende kemoterapi</td></tr></table></li><li>Include these codes as defined in <a href=\"CodeSystem-GenericValues.html\"><code>https://kip.rkkp.dk/fhir/CodeSystem/GenericValues</code></a><span title=\"Version is not explicitly stated, which means it is fixed to the version provided in this specification\"> version ?2.23.1</span><table class=\"none\"><tr><td style=\"white-space:nowrap\"><b>Code</b></td><td><b>Display</b></td><td><b>Definition</b></td></tr><tr><td><a href=\"CodeSystem-GenericValues.html#GenericValues-other\">other</a></td><td>Anden behandling</td><td>Other - used to choose unspecific value not in a valueset</td></tr></table></li></ul></div>"
